data.description: Welcome Home to This Charming Log Cabin Nestled on Five Acres of Land.  This 3 Bedroom, 2 Full Bath Ranch Offers Country Living with All the Privacy and Seclusion You Would Want.   Vaulted Living Room Ceilings with Open Kitchen with Island and Dining Room is the Perfect Layout for All Your Entertaining Needs. Appliances Remain including Washer Dryer Which is Located on the First Floor of the Kitchen.  The Oversized Back Deck Measures 17 X 10 and has a Great View of the Property.   The Lower-Level Features Two Bedrooms, a Full Bathroom plus a Full Kitchen Ideal for the Perfect Summer Cookouts and Gatherings.  Wood Burning Fireplace Located in the Family Room to Save on your Energy Cost.
